Suggests: python3-noisereduce, ydotool
Description: Offline voice transcription for Linux desktop
 WhisperAloud provides offline speech-to-text transcription using
 OpenAI Whisper. It runs as a D-Bus daemon with system tray integration,
 global hotkeys, and a GTK4 GUI.
 .
 Features include automatic gain control, noise gating, clipboard
 integration, and transcription history.
